lly.com/product/0636920028857.do\">Functional JavaScript</a> ‚àí Excellent book introduction concepts of functional programming with JavaScript, presented upon <em>Underscore.js</em>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://addyosmani.github.com/backbone-fundamentals/\">Developing Backbone.js applications</a> ‚àí An exhaustive guide to introduce you all the basics you‚Äôll need to develop with <em>Backbone.js</em>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/kjbekkelund/writings/blob/master/published/understanding-backbone.md/\">From jQuery to Backbone.js</a> ‚àí A <em>jQuery</em> code turned into <em>Backbone.js</em> logic, step by step.</p>\n<h2 id=\"front-end-performance\"><a href=\"#front-end-performance\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Front-end performance</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://browserdiet.com/\">How to lose weight (in the browser)</a> ‚àí The definitive front-end performance guide for developers.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://csswizardry.com/2013/01/front-end-performance-for-web-designers-and-front-end-developers/\">Front-end performance by CSSWizardry</a> ‚àí Few thoughts from Harry Roberts about performance for web designers and front-end developers.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.igvita.com/posa/high-performance-networking-in-google-chrome/\">High Performance Networking in Chrome</a> ‚àí An interesting article about Google Chrome performance. Little bit technical but worth reading.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Worth reading","date":null,"description":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/worth-reading"}}